uk.gov.gchq.palisade.config.service.request

Class GetConfigRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request.Request
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.config.service.request.GetConfigRequest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddConfigRequest

    public class GetConfigRequest
extends Request
    A request class that is sent by services and clients wanting their initial configuration data. The class has an Optional service field that is used to specify which Service to request the configuration for. If this is left empty, then the Palisade client configuration is requested, i.e. the "anonymous" configuration. Note that there may be additional authentication/authorisation constraints placed upon requestees. This means that for example, a client may not be able to request configuration details for a particular service.
